# Site conventions

## Structure

- Config: `site/src/config/site.ts` (URLs, contact, SEO, booking URL)
- Pages: `site/src/pages/` — `index.astro` (zh), `en/index.astro`
- Sections: one component per homepage block in `site/src/components/`
- Shared UI: `site/src/components/ui/`

## i18n

- All user-visible strings live in `site/src/i18n/zh.ts` and `en.ts`
- Do not hardcode copy in `.astro` files except structural markup
- Keep zh/en section keys aligned (tests in `site/src/i18n/`)

## Styling

- Tailwind 4 via `site/src/styles/global.css`
- Use design tokens from `website/design-brief.md`; avoid loud colors or cartoon styling
- Prefer existing component patterns over new abstractions

## Quality gates (before done)

```bash
cd site
npm test && npm run check && npm run build
# UI changes:
npm run test:e2e
```

## Security

- Static site only — no secrets, no server-side forms in repo
- External links: `rel="noopener noreferrer"`
